snippet.title: LionBricks
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel - my name's LionBricks. I'm a AFOL LEGO builder based in England.
I create LEGO MOCs, tutorials & city updates.
Have a look at my collection of MOCs on flickr: @LionBricks 
You can support my channel and see exclusive content on Patreon: www.patreon.com/user?u=30932662
